			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>This sturdy but worn scythe is carved with images of wheat sheaves, and the blade bears the image of a single rose.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Weapon</b><b>:</b> Scythe</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +1d6 critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Properties:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>For a character who is a member of a divine class or a primal class, this scythe functions as a staff implement.</li>\n<li>Whenever you use a healing power to allow an ally to regain hit points, until the end of your next turn, any creature that hits that ally with a melee attack takes damage equal to the scythe's enhancement bonus.</li>\n</ul></p>",
